{"type":"message","id":"b57575f3","parentId":"e7b4890f","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:48:18.098Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"要测试TUI（终端用户界面）连接，可以尝试以下几种方法：\n\n1. **使用 `ping` 命令**：测试网络连接是否正常。\n2. **使用 `ssh` 命令**：如果是远程连接，测试SSH是否可达。\n3. **使用 `curl` 或 `wget`**：测试HTTP/HTTPS服务的连通性。\n4. **使用 `telnet` 或 `nc`**：测试特定端口的连通性。\n\n请告诉我具体的连接目标（如IP地址、域名或服务），我可以帮助你执行相应的测试或提供进一步的指导。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"haihub","model":"DeepSeek-V3-0324","usage":{"input":15771,"output":125,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15896,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773496094836}}
