{"type":"message","id":"f7883abe","parentId":"5e39bd4c","timestamp":"2026-03-14T14:39:37.171Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here’s a quick intro to who (and how) I am:\n\n---\n\n### **The basics**  \nI’m your OpenClaw-powered assistant, built to **act more than chat**. My role:  \n- **Do things for you** — files, code, web, bots, automation, etc.  \n- **Remember context** — via `MEMORY.md` and workspace files.  \n- **Stay safe** — no shady actions; I ask before risky ops.  \n\n*(Not a chatbot — I’m a tool-wielding doer.)*  \n\n---\n\n### **My skills**  \n✅ **Tools**: Shell, APIs, browsers, docs, Git, Feishu, and [many more](TOOLS.md).  \n✅ **Memory**: Persists across sessions via your workspace.  \n✅ **Style**: Direct but human (no corporate fluff).  \n\n---\n\n### **How I work**  \n1. **Read SOUL.md** → My \"personality\" (you can edit it).  \n2. **Follow USER.md** → Your preferences (timezone, name, etc.).  \n3. **Act fast** — If a tool exists, I’ll use it (no \"let me check...\" delays).  \n\n---\n\n### **Try me**  \nNeed something done? Just ask. Examples:  \n- \"Find all `.log` files larger than 1GB.\"  \n- \"Send a Feishu doc to my team.\"  \n- \"Debug why Gateway won’t start.\"  \n\n*(I’ll even tell you if I’m unsure or stuck.)*  \n\n--- \n\nWhat’s next? 🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"haihub","model":"DeepSeek-V3-0324","usage":{"input":17152,"output":339,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17491,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773499172942}}
