{"type":"message","id":"65430b15","parentId":"e10a5736","timestamp":"2026-03-14T14:45:41.729Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"根据系统日志显示，Gateway 刚刚完成了重启和更新（`npm` 更新成功），且系统自动运行了 `openclaw doctor --non-interactive` 进行健康检查。这表明：  \n\n**✅ 当前状态**  \n- **版本**：你运行的 OpenClaw 实例已是最新版本（更新时间为 `2026-03-14 22:43:33 GMT+8`）。  \n- **健康检查**：`doctor` 命令已自动执行，若无错误输出，则基础功能正常。  \n\n如需进一步验证：  \n1. 手动检查版本号：  \n   bash\n   openclaw --version\n     \n2. 查看更新日志：  \n   bash\n   openclaw changelog --latest\n     \n\n需要我具体检查某项功能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"haihub","model":"DeepSeek-V3-0324","usage":{"input":22284,"output":175,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22459,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773499537133}}
